  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to look at how feasible it is to incorporate a state-of-the-art
      smoking cessation treatment program into community substance abuse treatment programs and its
      impact on substance abuse and cigarette smoking.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
