  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient is alcohol or drug dependent, in Outpatient Drug-Free or Opiate Substitute
             program and is interested in quitting smoking

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient is psychotic

          -  Use of smokeless tobacco

          -  Use of other smoking cessasation product

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Patient has hyper-tension, heart problems, or skin condition
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
